https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tim-burgess">Tim Burgess</a>推出了一款旅行包，其灵感来自于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-charlatans">The Charlatans</a>的单曲“How High”。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/opinion/twitter-listening-parties-time-burgess-lockdown-anniversary-2905075"><b>在封锁的一年里，蒂姆的 Twitter 聆听派对一直是欢乐的源泉</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>新设计标志着这位独立主唱与曼彻斯特品牌 Hikerdelic 之间的最新合作——灵感源自该乐队 1997 年专辑“Telling Stories”中的单曲。</p><p>据新闻稿称，该包的设计融入了数十年的巡演经验，并根据 Burgess 的巡演时间而设计。</p><p>至于规格，Hikerdelic 和主唱都表示，它的设计考虑到了“最大的可访问性和适应性”——其特色包括品牌饮水瓶、充电宝和指定隔间。它也由军用级 400D 尼龙制成，颜色与“How High”系列之前版本的颜色相匹配，并在其中一个隔层中印有手写歌词。 </p><figure id="attachment_3588516" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3588516" style="width: 1990px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3588516" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TimBurgess-Hikerdelic@2000.jpg" alt="Tim Burgess X Hikerdelic 旅行包。" width="1990" height="2548" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TimBurgess-Hikerdelic@2000.jpg 1990w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TimBurgess-Hikerdelic@2000-400x512.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TimBurgess-Hikerdelic@2000-800x1024.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TimBurgess-Hikerdelic@2000-696x891.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TimBurgess-Hikerdelic@2000-1392x1782.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TimBurgess-Hikerdelic@2000-1068x1367.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1990px) 100vw, 1990px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3588516" class="wp-caption-text"> Tim Burgess X Hikerdelic 旅行包。图片来源：Hikerdelic </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3588504" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3588504" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3588504" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic-2@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Tim Burgess X Hikerdelic 旅行包" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic-2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic-2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic-2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic-2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic-2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic-2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3588504" class="wp-caption-text"> Tim Burgess X Hikerdelic 旅行包。图片来源：Hikerdelic</figcaption></figure><p>据报道，这款包“制作了 30 年，又开发了两年”，专为长时间旅行而设计，伯吉斯已经在 The Charlatans 的英国、美国、爱尔兰和欧洲巡演中使用过。</p><p>该包将于 3 月 1 日发售，售价 125 英镑。您可以<a href="https://hikerdelic.com/blogs/news/coming-soon-hikerdelic-x-tim-burgess-how-high-tour-bag" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到更多详细信息并查看下面的设计图片。 </p><figure id="attachment_3588508" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3588508" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3588508" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic3.jpg" alt="Tim Burgess X Hikerdelic 旅行包。" width="2000" height="2500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic3-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Burgess-Hikerdelic3-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2